                    At our restaurant, we love to treat our valued customers to special offers and sales that make dining with us even more enjoyable.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="Outline">
                <img
                    src="/images/index-images/calendar.png.crdownload"
                    alt="Image 3"
                />
                <h2>No commitment whatsoever</h2>
                <p>
                    We understand that flexibility is key, which is why our offers and promotions come with no strings attached.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="Outline">
                <img
                    src="/images/index-images/freshfood.webp"
                    alt="Image 3"
                />
                <h2>Fresh Food</h2>
                <p>
                    At our restaurant, we pride ourselves on serving fresh, high-quality food that delights your taste buds and nourishes your body.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="oval-background">
        <img
            src="/images/index-images/chef.png"
            alt="Your Image"
            class="center-image"
            id="ii"
        />
    </div>
    <div class="content-left">
            <h1>
                Cooked By the <br />
                Best Chefs
            </h1>
            <p>
                Our chefs are passionate culinary professionals dedicated to crafting delicious and innovative dishes.<br>
                 With diverse backgrounds and a wealth of experience, <br>
                 they bring unique flavors and techniques to our kitchen.<br>
                  Each chef is committed to using fresh, high-quality ingredients to create meals<br>
